Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.43,0:00:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想打從心裡大叫一句\N好想快點見到妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.18,0:00:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信總有一天\N一定能相遇相知永結連理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.99,0:00:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起步走出\N希望妳能追著我的背影而來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.44,0:00:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我孤單一人只為等候妳的到來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.42,0:01:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,落英繽紛的春日午後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.43,0:01:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我將祈禱轉為誓言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.37,0:01:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但願妳不會忘記最重要的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.64,0:01:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永遠閃亮動人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.05,0:01:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝太多的話,開車不太好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.86,0:01:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了早上酒就會醒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.53,0:01:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經訂好房間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.77,0:01:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三…三鷹…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.54,0:01:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果今晚不行的話\N明天我也會訂房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.37,0:01:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後天也會訂,大後天也會\N這樣一直訂下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.05,0:02:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到妳對我打開心扉為止\N我會一直訂下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.66,0:02:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#84 1000%的嫌疑\N響子的緋聞之夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.44,0:02:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太晚了,響子到底到哪裡去了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.68,0:02:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚我不會讓她回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.22,0:02:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果三鷹是當真的\N我在這裡等也沒有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.26,0:02:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裕作,你打算等到什麼時候?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.63,0:02:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.49,0:02:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這兩個孩子拜託妳照顧\N我出去一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.53,0:02:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出去?你要去哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.93,0:02:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.87,0:02:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.51,0:02:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.04,0:03:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伯…伯父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.08,0:03:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有話想跟響子說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.51,0:03:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我自己進去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.02,0:03:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員還沒回來喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.05,0:03:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.79,0:03:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她應該還跟三鷹在一起吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.33,0:03:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是大驚小怪\N才九點半而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.56,0:03:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.27,0:03:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然把我女兒拖到半夜\N還不讓她回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.21,0:03:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子,等著吧\N爸爸馬上去救妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.35,0:03:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點走吧,伯父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.95,0:03:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伯父?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.16,0:03:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.71,0:04:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹,你這麼做讓我很為難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.52,0:04:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道這種做法非常粗暴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.62,0:04:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是在開玩笑吧,因為…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.02,0:04:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳看這是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.43,0:04:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們房間的鑰匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.43,0:04:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來只要…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.50,0:04:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果能找到開啟\N妳心扉的鑰匙就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.64,0:04:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是說,必須硬把它撬開呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.15,0:04:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.72,0:04:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.50,0:05:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是該怎麼說才好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.63,0:05:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曖昧的逃走也解決不了事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.05,0:05:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹,你聽我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.65,0:05:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們出去吹吹夜風吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.39,0:05:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.47,0:05:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像不在的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.77,0:05:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知不知道\N他們還會在其它什麼地方嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.31,0:05:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.61,0:05:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.91,0:05:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之,到三鷹可能去的地方\N找找看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.35,0:05:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留在這裡也沒有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.69,0:06:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.53,0:06:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想打個電話回一刻館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.63,0:06:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢?妳又不是小孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.93,0:06:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為大家可能會擔心我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.57,0:06:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳又想叫五代出來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.34,0:06:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,猜對了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.14,0:06:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不會,我才不會做這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.61,0:06:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.85,0:06:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟這是我跟妳的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.53,0:06:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了來了,來了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.90,0:06:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,一刻館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.30,0:06:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.24,0:06:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一之瀨太太,我還在外面…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.51,0:06:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊,妳慢慢玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.81,0:06:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有什麼人\N有什麼急事找我呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.35,0:07:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.35,0:07:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,五代呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.39,0:07:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?五代?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.36,0:07:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道耶,他好像出門去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.53,0:07:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳找他有事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.80,0:07:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有,沒事,那我掛斷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.00,0:07:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼搞的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.30,0:07:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候,他跑到哪裡去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.14,0:07:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定,他是出來找我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.41,0:07:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他去哪裡找了呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.40,0:07:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有想到什麼可能的地方?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.70,0:07:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.04,0:08:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生,這裡不能抽煙啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.21,0:08:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.31,0:08:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.05,0:08:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噁心的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.05,0:08:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噁心的地方?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.72,0:08:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯,有美麗的夜景
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.99,0:08:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,氣氛浪漫的酒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.29,0:08:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以看得見海的公園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.29,0:08:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此,果然很噁心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.39,0:08:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.29,0:08:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,動作快一點,快一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.84,0:08:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服的風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.28,0:08:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會不會冷?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.12,0:08:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會,倒是你的酒醒了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.97,0:09:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼做,才能不傷害到我\N又能拒絕我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.61,0:09:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是在想這個嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.85,0:09:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不論妳怎麼做,都很殘酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.89,0:09:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很殘酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.10,0:09:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.24,0:09:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.07,0:09:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道這不是道歉\N就能解決的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.74,0:09:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我實在是太隨便了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.58,0:09:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.65,0:09:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在事情發展到這樣之前…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.69,0:09:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.96,0:10:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.47,0:10:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要露出這樣的表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.65,0:10:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果能像這樣\N也能擁抱住妳的心的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.76,0:10:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.33,0:10:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚我會取消的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.41,0:10:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有辦法送妳回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.21,0:10:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為看到妳的臉,我會覺得很痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.20,0:11:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員到底在哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.04,0:11:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,天都快亮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.44,0:11:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我累了,回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.58,0:11:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想再稍微找一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.39,0:11:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼這麼拼命呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.43,0:11:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說這個,你聽了或許會生氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.87,0:11:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我想跟響子結婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.99,0:12:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伯父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.43,0:12:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伯父,你怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.80,0:12:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伯父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.00,0:12:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果能像這樣\N也能擁抱住妳的心的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.32,0:13:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代到底到哪裡去了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.39,0:13:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伯父,不要這麼衝動嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.96,0:13:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少囉嗦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.83,0:13:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然一整晚跟男人在夜遊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.57,0:13:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到她,我一定要給她一巴掌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.30,0:13:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以使用暴力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.94,0:13:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且管理員不是那種人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.27,0:13:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不用替她說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.47,0:13:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩個成熟的男女\N一整晚都在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.01,0:13:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能什麼事都沒做呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.71,0:13:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且對方是\N那個叫三鷹的男人喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.62,0:13:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定會有什麼事!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.75,0:13:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.13,0:13:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.27,0:13:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.67,0:14:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會來這裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.31,0:14:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳還問我為什麼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.14,0:14:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伯父,冷靜下來慢慢說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.88,0:14:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,你聽到了吧\N還虧我們找了她一整晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.01,0:14:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子,妳實在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.62,0:14:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起,讓你擔心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.82,0:14:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啦,結果,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.66,0:14:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事…都沒發生吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.83,0:14:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是指什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.17,0:14:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個…那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.60,0:14:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之,爸爸很相信妳喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.04,0:14:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.28,0:14:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,回家睡個覺吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.62,0:14:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一直跟我爸爸在一起嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.19,0:15:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.56,0:15:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳爸爸很有意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.40,0:15:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.03,0:15:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.74,0:15:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳昨晚幾點回來的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.44,0:15:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概兩點左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.01,0:15:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有點回來晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.18,0:15:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.25,0:15:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害你擔心了,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.09,0:15:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.66,0:15:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.19,0:15:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為妳到很晚還沒回來\N我擔心妳會發生什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.46,0:15:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,我說的“什麼事”\N沒有別的意思喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.50,0:15:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,就算有什麼事\N我也不會在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.60,0:15:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,我進去睡一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.51,0:15:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.58,0:15:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之,平安無事回來就好\N平安無事就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.05,0:15:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.22,0:16:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的,明明就很在意嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.73,0:16:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對方是三鷹\N她回來的時間又那麼晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.91,0:16:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩點啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.18,0:17:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.99,0:17:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.62,0:17:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.56,0:17:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太郎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.84,0:17:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.51,0:17:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,部長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.15,0:17:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天好溫暖喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.32,0:17:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽今天一定會回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.25,0:17:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,我夢見媽媽回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.76,0:17:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊,那個夢一定會成真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.36,0:17:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的,霞姊知不知道\N自己是個母親啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.17,0:17:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孩子明明那麼相信她\N一直在等她回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.09,0:18:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天感覺好安靜喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.29,0:18:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,因為大家都還在睡覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.69,0:18:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚好像在四谷的房間\N開了宴會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.36,0:18:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.04,0:19:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,部長,打起精神來\N我媽媽一定會回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.08,0:19:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起,對不起,不是的\N我不是在說你媽媽的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.15,0:19:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好羨慕太郎的媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.88,0:19:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為太郎完全相信她\N一直在這裡等她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.59,0:19:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也曾經很相信妳啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.02,0:19:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,意思是你現在在懷疑我嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.29,0:19:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又沒有這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.16,0:19:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你明明就是在懷疑我嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.10,0:19:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,懷疑妳什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.54,0:19:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚,我跟三鷹去飯店…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.35,0:19:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在酒吧裡喝了一點酒\N欣賞海景
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.39,0:19:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有這樣而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.99,0:20:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你所想的事情,都沒有發生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.23,0:20:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說的是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.27,0:20:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.14,0:20:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.25,0:20:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的口氣好像不太好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.68,0:20:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.55,0:20:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我打從一開始就很相信妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.29,0:20:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不對?太郎\N相信的人才能獲得救贖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.32,0:20:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騙人,你明明就在懷疑我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.23,0:20:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,部長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.56,0:20:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽好慢喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.17,0:20:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.91,0:20:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萬一她不回來,該怎麼辦呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.41,0:20:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道該怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.68,0:20:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她一定會回來的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.55,0:20:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.45,0:20:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.86,0:21:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.53,0:21:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對喔,霞姊身上帶著呼叫器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.54,0:21:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在正在呼叫您撥的號碼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.91,0:21:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請掛上電話等候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.67,0:21:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太…太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.34,0:21:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太郎,不要哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.58,0:21:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼萬一的話\N部長會照顧你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.35,0:21:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.95,0:22:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心,媽媽一定會回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.46,0:22:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,霞姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.93,0:22:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太郎,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.77,0:22:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.91,0:22:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的,男孩子怎麼哭成這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.14,0:22:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳什麼時候去二樓的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.01,0:22:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我昨晚就一直待在二樓啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.91,0:22:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為不忍心叫醒太郎他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.35,0:22:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以到隔壁房間去喝酒\N結果居然睡著了,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.25,0:22:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,妳是管理員吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.42,0:22:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳這麼照顧我的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.03,0:22:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.46,0:22:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會,初次見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.84,0:22:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了,太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.87,0:22:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花子一定也很高興吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.74,0:23:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太郎,你很擔心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.04,0:23:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然會擔心囉,拖到這麼晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.78,0:23:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是你相信媽媽對不對\N太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.23,0:23:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.66,0:23:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.10,0:23:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙的個性就是這樣\N妳也吃了不少苦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.97,0:23:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.87,0:23:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然說什麼吃不吃苦的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.24,0:23:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶,妳在說什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.64,0:23:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟管理員是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.31,0:23:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是房客跟管理員的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.78,0:23:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以,不是那種…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.28,0:23:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.65,0:23:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.29,0:23:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代和三鷹教練決鬥?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.59,0:23:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真蠢,明天明明就要參加\N最重要的畢業考了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.63,0:24:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,他們兩人\N遲早也是要做個了斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.70,0:24:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.44,0:24:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,『關鍵時刻!\N五代和三鷹宿命的對決』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.54,0:24:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我絕不會把響子讓給你!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.48,0:24:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin the night
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.08,0:24:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin your love
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.22,0:24:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳該知道這不是擦身而過的戀情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.33,0:24:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親吻也是…woo
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.43,0:24:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳比我想像中冷淡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:39.67,0:24:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡一個人獨處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:43.24,0:24:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沉默不語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:48.18,0:24:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要逞強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:51.85,0:24:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這燭火依偎著的夜晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:02.06,0:25:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凝視著妳的一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:09.04,0:25:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,試著將至今的謊言吹熄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:16.91,0:25:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin the night
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:20.48,0:25:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin your love
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:23.75,0:25:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自我陶醉故弄玄虛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:28.02,0:25:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我行不通…woo
